metadata.name: 24ct Parrots #1
metadata.description: A collection of 10,000 Parrots living on the Etherium blockchain. These parrots have left their pirate masters and have gathered all the lost loot. Their goal is to share their plunder to improve the lives of animals all around the world. With every 24ct Parrot bought, 50% of all sales will be donated to the WWF.
